## 🔐 Security Concepts Demonstrated

| Concept | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Defense in Depth** | NSG rules restrict traffic at the network layer before it reaches the VM |
| **Least Privilege** | RBAC roles scoped to minimum required permissions at deployment time |
| **Configuration Consistency** | Scripted deployments eliminate human error that creates security gaps |
| **Audit Trail** | Version-controlled scripts create a documented record of every infrastructure change |
