## 📊 Deployment Workflow Summary

```
1. Authenticate  →  az login / service principal
2. Set scope     →  subscription + resource group
3. Network       →  VNet → Subnet → NSG → Rules
4. Compute       →  VM → OS → Size → Credentials
5. Security      →  NSG attach → RBAC assign
6. Validate      →  confirm resources + access
7. Cleanup       →  teardown script → cost control
```

